summary: The Huntsman House is a nice little house located at the beutiful lake of Falkreath. Just east of the Brittleshin Pass.
descriptionHtml:
The Huntsman House is a nice little house located at the beutiful lake of Falkreath. Just east of the Brittleshin Pass.

Interior and exterior is detailed, and you won't be able to push things around because, most of them are static. Why? Because i hate to walk around and accidently pick something up or push it around. You will find containers, custom crafting stations etc. 
Everything is placed with a sence for perfection to give you the best experience.

NOTE:
After watching the showcase movies i realized that some content is missing. I am working on it, so stay tuned for an update.
It will include more containers and more sceneri for both the interior and the exterior. Also fixes the floating items.

Known Bugs:
 - Weapon Plaque, it won't let you pick up your 1Handed weapon, all other weapons works just fine.
- Navmesh not working probably

CREDITS:
The TESA folks for Skyrim Resource Kit Project
And a great thanks to Lilith for the amazing meshes and textures

Please leave a comment on bugs or needs :)
This is my first mod so i appreciate all the feedback :)
Enjoy My Friends!
author: Mallick
